title: Can We Turn Resin Pigments Into PAINT?
author: EvanAndKatelyn
description:
Can we make paint using our resin colorants?? Thanks to our sponsor Squarespace, go to https://www.squarespace.com/evanandkatelyn for 10% off your first purchase. Check out the tools/materials we used below! 👇

Check out the Patreon Aftershow for:
• What the heck happened to the gold alcohol ink??
• Other things we can use the vibrator for (don't be dirty)
• Other combinations we want to try
• Comparing this video to our pigment mixing video
• Any other fun art experiments we could do?
